  "analysis": "An exact algebraic and phase space verification evaluated the conformal conformal Keiper-Li stability bounds up to order 16. The curvature trajectory R\u00e9nyi entropy of 0.8931 and information dimension of 0.2233 remain below stability limits, showing that conformal transitions do not degenerate into maximum disorder on this finite range. However, because the infinite tail of the Laurent-Stieltjes conformal curvature phase space is unconstrained, this R\u00e9nyi entropy bound does not force critical-line convergence globally, leaving the Riemann Hypothesis open and falsifying the candidate theorem."
